WEBVTT
Kind: captions
Language: en-GB

00:00:12.790 --> 00:02:51.930
10) Police in Florida arrested a 90-year-old
WWII veteran. His crime was feeding homeless

00:02:51.930 --> 00:02:52.930
people in public.

00:02:52.930 --> 00:02:53.930
9) 7-year-old Poppy Burge was given a boob
job voucher for her birthday. The present

00:02:53.930 --> 00:02:54.930
was from her mum, a plastic surgery addict
known as The Human Barbie.

00:02:54.930 --> 00:02:55.930
8) Police in Iowa shut down a 4-year-old’s
lemonade stand. The stand was a violation

00:02:55.930 --> 00:02:56.930
as the child didn’t have a permit.

00:02:56.930 --> 00:02:57.930
7) A Wal-Mart worker was trampled to death
by Black Friday shoppers. 2,000 customers

00:02:57.930 --> 00:02:58.930
smashed through the store front, lifting the
doors off their hinges.

00:02:58.930 --> 00:02:59.930
6) A doctor who killed a pensioner was called
an 'animal' by the victim's son. The doctor

00:02:59.930 --> 00:03:00.930
sued over the insult &amp; won - the son had to
pay the doctor's court costs &amp; write a letter

00:03:00.930 --> 00:03:01.930
of apology.

00:03:01.930 --> 00:03:02.930
5) 18-year-old Rachel Canning moved out &amp; then
tried to sue her parents for support &amp; college

00:03:02.930 --> 00:03:03.930
tuition. She left because she didn’t want
to keep a curfew or do chores.

00:03:03.930 --> 00:03:04.930
4) A woman owed more than $50,000 &amp; faced
bankruptcy after having a heart attack &amp; slipping

00:03:04.930 --> 00:03:05.930
into a coma. The ambulance had taken her to
a hospital that wasn’t covered by her insurance.

00:03:05.930 --> 00:03:06.930
3) A 25-year-old nurse lied to police, claiming
her grandfather had raped her. She thought

00:03:06.930 --> 00:03:07.930
if he was in prison, she’d get her inheritance
early.

00:03:07.930 --> 00:03:08.930
2) Eric Garner died after cops threw him to
the ground in a chokehold. Minutes before

00:03:08.930 --> 00:03:09.930
he had been breaking up a fight.

00:03:09.930 --> 00:03:10.930
1) Wang Yue was left dying in the road after
she was run over by 2 vans. 18 pedestrians

00:03:10.930 --> 00:03:10.940
walked passed the 2-year-old's bloody body
&amp; failed to help her.

